data.title: Favara, Valencia, Spain
data.text:
Favara, also known as Favareta, is a municipality located in the province of Valencia, Spain, with coordinates 39.1166700 latitude and -0.2833300 longitude. The weather in Favara is characterized by hot summers and mild winters, with an average temperature of 17.5°C. Favara has a rich history and heritage, dating back to the Roman era. It was once an important agricultural center, and its legacy can still be seen in the many orchards and vineyards that surround the town.
